import React from 'react'
import './index.css'


import { Switch, Route } from 'react-router-dom'
import Homepage from './Homepage'
import Test from './Test'

const App = () => {
  return(
  <>
      <Switch>
    <Route exact path = "/" component={Homepage}/>
    <Route exact path = "/test" component={Test}/>

    </Switch>
   
    </>
  )
}

export default App
